<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-09-28T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-09-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="357" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d357">
                    <note rend="inline" type="source">840.48 Refugees/4529</note>
                    <head>
                        <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss>
                            to the British Chargé</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Campbell</hi></persName>)</head>
                    <opener>
                        <dateline rendition="#right">
                            <placeName>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-09-28">September 28,
                            1943</date>.</dateline>
                    </opener>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">My Dear Mr. Chargé d’affaires</hi>: I have received
                        your letter of September 9, 1943 in regard to the decision of your
                        Government to <pb facs="0366" n="356" xml:id="pg_356"/> accept for onward
                        transport to Palestine all Jews who may succeed in escaping to Turkey from
                        enemy-controlled territory.</p>
                    <p>I assume that the British Ambassador at Ankara will be informed of this
                        decision and hope that it will be possible for him to communicate it
                        informally to the American Embassy at Ankara. Such action would be of great
                        assistance in connection with our joint efforts to relieve the sufferings of
                        these unfortunate people.</p>
                    <p>Sincerely yours,</p>
                    <closer>
                        <signed>A. A. <hi rend="smallcaps">Berle, Jr.</hi>
                        </signed>
                    </closer>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>